title: The-Laura-Ingraham-Show-Podcast May 12 2016
description:
Laura Ingraham Podcast May 12, 2016


Michael Goodwin - New York Post Columnist, Fox News Contributor "The American people who like trump look past all of this as noise" Sam Carpenter - First real challenge to Sen. Ron Wyden (D) in Oregon in the general election; multi-business owner from Bend, Oregon. "Somebody's got to turn the apple cart over" Jay Carafano - Director of the Center for Foreign Policy Studies and the deputy director of the Institute for International Studies at The Heritage Foundation on Obama's Japan visit "It's just one embarrassment after the next" 



Thursday, May 12, 2016

Guest Lineup

Michael Goodwin - New York Post Columnist, Fox News Contributor
Sam Carpenter - First real challenge to Sen. Ron Wyden (D) in Oregon in the general election; multi-business owner from Bend, Oregon
Jay Carafano - Director of the Center for Foreign Policy Studies and the deputy director of the Institute for International Studies at The Heritage Foundation
Gene Kopelson - Author of Reagan's 1968 Dress Rehearsal: Ike, RFK, and Reagan's Emergence as a World Statesman




Ingraham says Trump Tax returns only matter to Hillary and maybe Mitt Romney
